solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public int firstUniqChar(String s) {--newline--        int freq [] = new int[26];--newline--        for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i ++)--newline--            freq [s.charAt(i) - 'a'] ++;--newline--        for(int i = 0; i < s.length(); i ++)--newline--            if(freq [s.charAt(i) - 'a'] == 1)--newline--                return i;--newline--        return -1;--newline--    }--newline--}--newline--
